# Walkthrough - Responsive Reviews Grid

Implemented responsive design updates for the `[ocean_reviews_grid_test]` shortcode to improve readability on smaller screens.

## Changes

Modified [inc/reviews-test.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/ocean/wp-content/themes/hello-elementor-child/inc/reviews-test.php) to include specific media queries.

### Responsive Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Device Target | Font Size (Text) | Font Size (Author) | Card Padding |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **> 1500px** | Default / Large | 20px | 20px | 40px |
| **1251px - 1500px** | Laptop | 18px | 20px | 35px |
| **768px - 1250px** | Tablet | 17px | 18px | 30px |
| **< 767px** | Mobile | 15px | 16px | 20px |

### Code Updates

Refactored the `<style>` block to organize breakpoints and override base styles appropriately.

```css
        /* Laptop (1251px - 1500px) */
        @media (max-width: 1500px) {
            .ocean-review-card { padding: 35px; }
            .ocean-review-text { font-size: 18px; }
            /* ... */
        }

        /* Tablet (768px - 1250px) */
        @media (max-width: 1250px) {
            .ocean-review-card { padding: 30px; }
            .ocean-review-text { font-size: 17px; }
            /* ... */
        }

        /* Mobile (< 767px) */
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
             /* Stack columns, hide arrows, smaller text */
            .ocean-reviews-slide { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .ocean-review-card { padding: 20px; }
            .ocean-review-text { font-size: 15px; }
            /* ... */
        }
```

## Verification

The styles are applied directly within the shortcode output, ensuring no caching issues with external CSS files for this specific component.
User should verify on:
1.  **Mobile**: Check that cards stack (1 column) and text is readable (15px).
2.  **Tablet**: Check 2 column grid with slightly smaller text (17px).
3.  **Laptop**: Check transition at 1500px.
